ss=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564da1731169ba2f44522bce97f1ab879d20f14f","tid":332456,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:00:34.000Z","msg":"豆"},{"pid":"1a55f81ed91da1d0c6d4c87645f5822c585b4de3","tid":332456,"uid":18737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:59:37.000Z","msg":"單松<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b5d3d1f04e55cbeceacfc65ad3559e21e92c03","tid":332456,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T06:07:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廉價茶葉席捲廣州酒樓大排檔<br />\n2016/08/29 21:32<br />\n有線電視新聞台記者早前到位於廣州、全國最大的茶葉批發城，發現不少茶檔專門批發平價茶葉予酒樓和大排檔，最低五元一斤，業內人士指比成本價更低。有茶檔老闆坦言不敢飲用。 <br />\n<br />\n水熱茶香，泡一壼好茶，來個「一盅兩件」，真是愜意。但各間茶樓即使同一款茶，味道都可以很不同，到底茶葉從哪裡來的呢？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廣州芳村茶葉城是全國最大茶葉批發零售市場，很多都專門批發廉價茶葉。但一袋袋標榜來自雲南的普洱，一樣數元一斤有交易，店主還稱熟客多的是。她更即場泡茶，證明就算是廉價茶也茶色十足，不過她只泡給我們喝，她自己一口也沒喝。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這裡有逾千間茶葉專賣店，都是做批發生意，有線電視新聞記者問過其中不少店舖，有很多都表示有賣數元一斤的茶葉，有店主甚至坦言這種廉價茶莫說是喝，連用來洗碗也不敢。有線電視新聞記者問過酒樓負責人，他一樣很坦白，有內地記者將三款H數元一斤的廉價鐵觀音和普洱交由專家化驗。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二手茶即是將被棄置、泡過的茶葉，回收、加工再出售，沒廠家、沒品牌，沒檢測報告，食用安全及衛生成疑。廣州二手茶市場過去曾多次被揭發查封，都仍然賣得成行成市。</blockquote><br />\n香港啲酒樓老細出名仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd1be015ddcfab2d6b43038592f63b27a0d822b","tid":332456,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T06:11:24.000Z","msg":"一定飲壽眉"},{"pid":"b169099acb0d337943b88be3211720cca1d007e9","tid":332456,"uid":42190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T06:11:36.000Z","msg":"從來去飲菜都係帶自己茶葉 出面個啲茶葉好差"},{"pid":"9a4d1228beb7d411f97af07af6952954f16130c5","tid":332456,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T06:24:32.000Z","msg":"做過好多間好多<br />\n鐵觀音=水仙<br />\n壽眉=香片<br />\n都係好澀<br />\n普洱叫有味<br />\n但未必好飲<br />\n可以試下菊花/菊普<br />\n不過唔係間間有<br />\n最好自己帶菜葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31632d3b4b670b192f6a6178adecad4f49b9263c","tid":332456,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:08:38.000Z","msg":"自己帶茶葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThx下次飲茶參考一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea0eb4fd4125f73582b32ca22403568c739ef7f","tid":332456,"uid":2151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:18:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己帶茶葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThx下次飲茶參考一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n靚既龍井 鐵觀音 烏龍"},{"pid":"811ad9249d2b2309e9fd9116c2a2d03110061e80","tid":332456,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:28:36.000Z","msg":"飲開普洱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3cda010a7857b27f469271d1720da58e69bd62d","tid":332456,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T08:22:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"087a85a12a0f2e0c8dd4af83b55a451712a6c69c","tid":332456,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T08:23:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca3f566fa5fa2436465faeec2a447f4121e407df","tid":332456,"uid":2151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T09:27:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>水仙咪鐵觀音囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 Google完好似7左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三仙間廣東名門D鐵觀音好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922e2f471b6b9cf70f5e7f825ddcbf2e1b196db7","tid":332456,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:43:05.0